571. Thunder and rain befall you just as you pass by an ivy-covered church.
572. It becomes intensely silent. The effect ends abruptly if one steps beyond a certain area.
573. A man staggers down the road toward the party. Before he gets to them, he collapses onto the ground.
574. A vagabond, smelling strongly of alcohol, claims to be a god and demands the PCs worship him.
