746. A tree falls over with great force in front of you, another falls behind at the same time.
747. Ravagers assault a merchant's caravan.
748. Bathing in the stream was a good idea but the bubbles appearing are not yours.
749. A dead minotaur sprawls at the side of the road, a huge axe buried in its back.
750. A castle wall with just a crater inside.
751. A couple of rats start following.
752. A fat farmer and his plump daughter struggle with a broken wheel on his laden wagon full of turnip greens.
753. Fool's gold sparkles in the dirt.
